.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Flower: dahlia, azalea, iris, balloon-flower, aconite
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Cigar: dahliamaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Nationality:british == Flower:iris
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Nationality:danish == Beverage:tea
4. Flower:azalea is on the left of Flower:balloon-flower
5. Flower:azalea == Beverage:coffee
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Pet:bird
7. Flower:aconite == Cigar:dunhill
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:dahliamaster == Beverage:beer
13. Nationality:german == Cigar:prince
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Flower:dahlia
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Flower		|    aconite	|     dahlia	|      iris	|     azalea	|     balloon-flower	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   dahliamaster	|
